<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Ἀπία </supplied><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/> Σεραπιάδι τῇ κυρίᾳ 

    <lb n="2"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τρ</unclear>ὶ                   χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πολλά σε ἀσπάζομαι, κυρία, εὐχο-

    <lb n="4"/>μένη σοι τὰ κάλλιστα. κόμισαι, 

    <lb n="5"/>κυρία, <add place="supralinear">παρὰ τῆς ἠπητρίας</add> τὰ κρόκινα <choice><corr>ὀθονίδια</corr><sic>οθονειδια</sic></choice> τῆς 

    <lb n="6"/>θυγατρός σου, χιτῶνα καὶ <app type="BL"><lem resp="3.139">ἡρα-

    <lb n="7"/>τιανόν</lem><rdg>ηραχιανον</rdg></app>, καὶ Ἡρακλάμμωνι 

    <lb n="8"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>τῶνα. <subst><add place="inline">νομίζω</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ομιζω</del></subst> δὲ ὅτι ἐπιγ<add place="supralinear">ν</add>ώσει 

    <lb n="9"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ποῖ</unclear>ά ἐστιν τὰ τῆς θυγατρός σου. 

    <lb n="10"/>αὐτὰ γὰρ εἰς ἀμφότερα <subst><add place="inline"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εἵ</unclear>λιξα</add><del rend="corrected"><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>λιξα</del></subst>. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἡ ἠπήτρια μεταδώσει σοι διὰ λόγων 

    <lb n="12"/>ὅσα αὐτῇ εἶπον. <choice><corr>λίαν</corr><sic>λειαν</sic></choice> γὰρ <choice><corr>ὀψέ</corr><sic>οψαι</sic></choice> σοι 

    <lb n="13"/>ταῦτα ἔγραψα. Ἄγαθος δὲ τῇ ἐνά-

    <lb n="14"/>τῃ τάχα πρὸς σὲ γείνεται ἐνέγ-

    <lb n="15"/>και σοί τινα πρὸς τὴν ἑορτήν. ὥσ-

    <lb n="16"/>τε, κυρία, <subst><add place="inline"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μὴ</unclear></add><del rend="corrected"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> μετεωρίζου, κα-

    <lb n="17"/>λῶς διάγομεν. <choice><corr>Σερῆνος</corr><sic>σερηνως</sic></choice> ὁ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱός 

    <lb n="18"/>σου πολλά σε <subst><add place="inline">ἀσπάζεται</add><del rend="corrected">ασπαζε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>αι</del></subst>, καὶ 

    <lb n="19"/>Λούκις καὶ Τεχῶσις καὶ τὰ παιδία 

    <lb n="20"/>καὶ <subst><add place="inline">Τααμόις</add><del rend="corrected">τααμ<gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del></subst> καὶ ο<add place="supralinear">ἱ</add> ἡμῶν πάντες. 

    <lb n="21"/>τοὺ<add place="supralinear">ς</add> ἡμῶ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> ἀσπάζομαι. Λουκάμ-

    <lb n="22"/>μωνα τὸν ἀδελφὸν πολλὰ ἀσ-

    <lb n="23"/>πάζομαι, οὗ δέομαι γράψαι 

    <lb n="24"/><choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>η</sic></choice> ἐκομίσατο τὸν χιτῶ-

    <lb n="25"/>να αὐτοῦ παρὰ τοῦ Λεύκου, ἐπεὶ 

    <lb n="26"/>Βηρύλλος ἐπελάθετο αὐτὸν ἆραι. 

    <lb n="27"/><subst><add place="inline">Ἀλέξανδρον</add><del rend="corrected">αλεξανδρος</del></subst> καὶ Κυριλλοῦν πολ-

    <lb n="28"/>λὰ ἀσπάζομαι. 

    <lb n="29"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="30"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Σεραπ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ιά</unclear>δι μητρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied>     <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">παρὰ</supplied> Ἀπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ία</unclear>ς. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="300" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1679</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">31787</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">14</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1679</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;14;1679" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2006), S. 352</bibl><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2008), B6.2, Nr. 246</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31787" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>